@startuml
title Feedback Submission Sequence
actor User
participant Client
participant FeedbackController
participant FeedbackApplicationService
database PostgreSQL
User -> Client : submit feedback
Client -> FeedbackController : POST /api/feedback
FeedbackController -> FeedbackApplicationService : submitFeedback
FeedbackApplicationService -> PostgreSQL : save feedback
FeedbackController --> Client : 200 OK
@enduml
